rces/63696/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/63696/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-06-24","General Practitioners: South Lakeland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what the additional need weighting is for each GP surgery in South Lakeland.","false","Biography information for Tim Farron","Westmorland and Lonsdale","Tim Farron","202030"
